                    <p>Prices on our site are shown in United States dollars and are per traveler unless otherwise stated. The price shown at the moment you confirm your booking is the price you pay, even if our published price changes later.</p>
                    <p>We accept major credit and debit cards through our PCI DSS compliant payment processor. By providing payment information, you authorize us to charge the total amount shown at checkout, including any taxes and fees. We do not store full card numbers on our servers.</p>
                    <p>Currency conversions, foreign transaction fees, and similar charges levied by your bank are your responsibility.</p>
                </section>

