                    <h3>Cancellations you initiate</h3>
                    <p>Unless otherwise stated on the specific trip page, our standard cancellation policy is:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>More than 30 days before departure: full refund, minus any non-recoverable third party fees that we disclose to you in advance.</li>
                        <li>15 to 30 days before departure: 50 percent refund.</li>
                        <li>Less than 15 days before departure: no refund, except as required by law.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Cancellations we initiate</h3>
                    <p>If we cancel a trip (for example, due to safety, weather, or a partner unable to host), we refund you in full. We will make a reasonable effort to offer a comparable alternative trip, but we are not obligated to do so.</p>
                </section>

